<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179468>
    bibo:endPage "61" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "39" ;
    bibo:volume "1633" ;
    dc:creator "Kment, Petr; Bryja, Josef" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Description of Nasocoris lautereri sp. nov. from the Balkan peninsula, with a review of the genus Nasocoris (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Miridae: Phylinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179469>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179470>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179472>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179471> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179469>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Nasocoris lautereri sp. nov., habitus. 1 – Male, holotype (Greece, Poros Isl.) (3.7 mm); 2 – Female, paratype (Greece, Poros Isl.) (3.6 mm); 3 – Female (Croatia, Braċ Isl.) (3.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179469/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179470>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Nasocoris lautereri sp. nov., aedeagus (paratype from Greece, Poros Isl.). Scale bar = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179470/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179472>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 9. 7 – Nasocoris argyrotrichus Reuter, 1879, habitus. Female (Kazakhstan, Dzhambul region, Karasay env.) (3.3 mm); 8 – N. platycranoides Montandon, 1890, habitus. Female (Spian, Pizarra) (4.9 mm); 9 – N. tesquorum Kerzhner, 1970, habitus. Male, paratype (Kazakhstan, Dzhungarsky Alatau, Topolevka) (4.6 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179472/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179471>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 6. 5 (above) – Vidova Gora Mt. (top with the broadcaster; Croatia, Braċ Is., 780 m a. s. l.) (Photo: Jitka Schlägelová, September 2005), 6 (below) – Ephedra distachya L. growth under the top of Vidova Gora Mt., the second known locality of Nasocoris lautereri sp. nov. (Photo: P. Kment, September 2004)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

